metadata.name: Cosmic Angel
metadata.description:
Introducing the Cosmic Angel NFT Series - a groundbreaking collection of NFT 'Phygital' Pieces that offer the ultimate fusion of digital art and physical merchandise.

Each NFT in this series is a masterpiece, with intricate design details that capture the essence of ethereal entities. 

As a proud owner of this NFT, you'll be the only one in the world to have this 1/1 NFT both in the physical and metaverse realm. The Cosmic Angel Series offers unparalleled diversity in its outputs, ensuring that each buyer receives a completely unique and personalized version of their NFT.

To make this series even more special, each purchase comes with a physical print that can be displayed as canvas or metal art. This physical print serves as a tangible reminder of the incredible value and uniqueness of your NFT.
